pokedexEntries.red: Often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed, they quickly gather and attack in swarms.
pokedexEntries.blue: Often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed, they quickly gather and attack in swarms.
pokedexEntries.yellow: The heads attract each other and spin around. There must be 6 heads for it to maintain balance.
pokedexEntries.gold: The shell is very durable. Even if it cracks, it can survive without spilling the contents.
pokedexEntries.silver: Using telepathy only they can receive, they always form a cluster of six Exeggcute.
pokedexEntries.crystal: If even one is separated from the group, the energy bond between the six will make them rejoin instantly.
pokedexEntries.ruby: This Pokémon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: This Pokémon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution.
pokedexEntries.emerald: It consists of six eggs that care for each other. The eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear, it is close to evolution.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: Even though it appears to be eggs of some sort, it was discovered to be a life-form more like plant seeds.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: It is often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed, they gather quickly and attack in swarms.
pokedexEntries.diamond: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.pearl: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.platinum: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: The shell is very durable. Even if it cracks, it can survive without spilling the contents.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Using telepathy only they can employ, they always form a cluster of six Exeggcute.
pokedexEntries.black: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.white: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.black2: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.white2: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.x: Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated.
pokedexEntries.y: Even though it appears to be eggs of some sort, it was discovered to be a life-form more like plant seeds.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: This Pokémon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: This Pokémon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution.
pokedexEntries.sun: Its six eggs use telepathy to communicate among themselves. It is believed to carry plant genes and the genes of other species.
pokedexEntries.moon: Six of them together form a full-fledged Pokémon. It's often hunted by Crabrawler, but uses psychokinesis to drive it off.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: Six of them form a single Pokémon. Should one of the six be lost, the next morning there will once more be six.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: Although they are the same size as other Exeggcute, the ones produced in Alola are quite heavy. Their shells are packed full.
